column7: Saxophone ensembles of all types performing a mixture of traditional and 20th-century music for soprano, alto, tenor, baritone, and bass saxophone. 1 undergraduate hour. 1 graduate hour. May be repeated to a maximum of 3 hours in the same term if topics vary for a total of 16 undergraduate hours, 12 graduate hours in separate terms. Prerequisite: Consent of instructor.
